OL,3,CBritish baby born in Turkey to receive
OL,4,Clife-saving medical care in Bristol
OL,6,FHis only hope lies in returning to the
OL,7,FUK for life-saving treatment.
OL,9,FAdam, a Bristol resident who works for
OL,10,Fa UK company, pays UK tax and National
OL,11,FInsurance, and has spent #38,000 of
OL,12,Fhis own savings on an air ambulance to
OL,13,Fbring his dying son home.
OL,15,FDiagnosed with heart failure within
OL,16,Fweeks of being born and admitted to
OL,17,Fintensive care twice, baby Maverick is
OL,18,Fnow in urgent need of a heart
OL,19,Ftransplant.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
