OL,3,CBritish baby born in Turkey to receive
OL,4,Clife-saving medical care in Bristol
OL,6,FBoth Newcastle Freeman Hospital and
OL,7,FGreat Ormond Street Hospital confirmed
OL,8,Fthey could treat Maverick, but advised
OL,9,Fhe should first be stabilised at
OL,10,FBristol Royal Hospital.
OL,12,FHowever, according to Mr Corin,
OL,13,FBristol Royal repeatedly refused to
OL,14,Faccept the infant, citing uncertainty
OL,15,Fover his NHS eligibility, despite
OL,16,FMaverick being a British citizen and
OL,17,FAdam providing extensive documentation
OL,18,Fincluding payslips, bank statements,
OL,19,Fand even contacting HMRC to prove his
OL,20,FNational Insurance contributions.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
