OL,3,CBritish baby born in Turkey to receive
OL,4,Clife-saving medical care in Bristol
OL,6,FFollowing an urgent public appeal and
OL,7,Fintervention from MP Andrew George,
OL,8,Fwho hand-delivered Maverick's medical
OL,9,Freports to Health Secretary Wes
OL,10,FStreeting's office, Bristol Royal
OL,11,FHospital reversed its decision.
OL,13,FIn a post on Facebook, Mr Corin wrote,
OL,14,F"We had calls from other NHS hospitals
OL,15,Fsaying they will accept. Bristol just
OL,16,Fcalled and said they can now accept
OL,17,FMav so we are so happy. I owe you all
OL,18,Fso much."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
