OL,3,CBritish baby born in Turkey to receive
OL,4,Clife-saving medical care in Bristol
OL,6,FThe family is now preparing to fly
OL,7,FMaverick back to the UK as quickly as
OL,8,Fpossible, where he will receive the
OL,9,Fspecialist care unavailable in Turkey.
OL,11,FProfessor Tim Whittlestone, Chief
OL,12,FMedical and Innovation Officer,
OL,13,FBristol NHS Group said:
OL,15,F"Following an urgent review by a
OL,16,Fsenior multi-disciplinary team, we
OL,17,Fhave agreed to accept Maverick as a
OL,18,Fpatient at UHBW.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
