OL,3,CBritish baby born in Turkey to receive
OL,4,Clife-saving medical care in Bristol
OL,6,F"If he is able to travel safely, our
OL,7,Fteams will do everything they can to
OL,8,Fensure he receives the best possible
OL,9,Fcare.
OL,11,F"As at all times throughout this
OL,12,Fprocess, our thoughts are firmly with
OL,13,FMaverick and his family.
OL,15,F"We understand the public interest in
OL,16,Fthis case, but we must respect patient
OL,17,Fconfidentiality and therefore cannot
OL,18,Fshare any additional details or
OL,19,Fcomment further."
